                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7628" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">SCLM-0173</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">3199 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数实融合，“砼”享未来：恒盛集团供应链数字化转型之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Integration of Digital Technology and the Real Economy, Enjoy the Concrete Future with Partners: Supply Chain Digital Transformation of Hengsheng Group </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山红梅，方静，王晓燕，程梦珍，陆恒，钱依丹</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安邮电大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陕西恒盛集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">信息管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">恒盛集团；供应链数字化转型；供应链协同；商砼企业；2023百优案例；西部专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Hengsheng Group; Supply chain digital transformation; Supply chain collaboration; Commercial concrete enterprises</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着新一轮技术革命浪潮的深入推进，数字经济在全球范围内呈现出快
速发展的态势，数字化转型成为推动经济增长和创新发展的重要力量。而传统
商品混凝土行业兼具生产制造与物流服务业双重特性，同时面临着产能过剩、
供需信息不对称、产业集中度低等痛点问题，严重制约着行业企业的发展。本
案例描述了作为陕西商砼行业头部企业的恒盛集团把握数字经济发展趋势，打
造了一个信息畅通、供需对接、资源共享、功能完善、服务协同的全产业链综
合服务平台——“商砼之家”，为原材料供应企业、商砼企业、建筑企业、重点
项目客户等提供商品混凝土的原材料供应、集采集销、智能物流调度、检验检
测、设备租赁、安全监测、供应链金融等一站式服务，全面优化资源要素配置
效率，从根本上实现降本增效和服务升级，促进数字经济与实体经济、传统产
业与互联网产业的深度融合发展。本案例旨在引导学生学习数字经济背景下传
统实体行业供应链数字化转型的关键要素和实施路径，进而为新时期供应链数
字化赋能传统实体企业转型升级和高层次创新人才培养提供有益范例与启发性
思考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the deepening of a new wave of technological revolution, the digital
economy is showing a trend of rapid development worldwide. Digital transformation
has become an important force to promote economic growth and innovative
development. However, the traditional commodity concrete industry has a dual nature
of production and logistics services, while facing pain points such as excess
production capacity, asymmetry of supply and demand information, and low industry
concentration, severely restricting the development of industry enterprises. which
seriously restricts the development of industry enterprises. This case describes how
Hengsheng Group, the leading enterprise in the Shaanxi commercial concrete industry,grasps the trend of integrating digital and real development, and creates a
comprehensive service platform for the entire industry chain- “Concrete Home”,
which is characterized by information communication, supply-demand connection,
shared resources, complete functionality and collaborative services. It provides one-
stop services such as centralized procurement and sales of raw materials and
commodity concrete, intelligent logistics scheduling, inspection and testing,
equipment rental, safety monitoring, and supply chain finance for raw material supply
enterprises, commercial concrete enterprises, construction enterprises, key project
customers, etc., comprehensively optimizing the efficiency of resource allocation,
fundamentally realizing cost reduction and efficiency increase, and promoting the
deep integration and interactive development of the digital economy and the real
economy, and traditional industries and the Internet industry. This case aims to guide
students to learn the key elements and implementation path of supply chain digital
transformation of traditional real industries in the context of digital economy, and then
provide useful examples and inspirational thinking for the new period of supply chain
digitalization to empower the transformation and upgrading of traditional entity
enterprise and the cultivation of high-level innovative talents.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《供应链管理》、《物流与供应链管理》、《企业战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">商品混凝土行业痛点；供应链数字化转型的实施途径；供应链协同的内涵；经济效益、社会效益和环境效益；商品混凝土行业的绿色低碳发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
